can't you?

548
00:39:26,363 --> 00:39:30,570
How long is a little?
And don't say two weeks again.

549
00:39:30,700 --> 00:39:34,280
Well, there's the War Widows' Revue,
the craft fair...

550
00:39:34,412 --> 00:39:36,035
