something a little more contemporary.

580
00:42:13,805 --> 00:42:16,589
Hilda and I seem to have a talent
for the can-can.

581
00:42:16,724 --> 00:42:19,722
The traditional can-can,
performed without underwear?

582
00:42:19,853 --> 00:42:23,301
Oh, Philip!
- Anything for you, Philip.

583
00:42:23,438 --> 00:42:25,144
Yes, anything.

584
00:42:25,273 --> 00:42:28,141
That'll raise a bit more than money
for the war widows.

585
00:42:28,277 --> 00:42:31,725
I'm doubling my donation.
- Oh, Pinkie.

586
00:42:31,862 --> 00:42:34,148
Fans at the ready, gentlemen!

587
00:42:34,282 --> 00:42:37,398
All the way from gay Paris,

588
00:42:37,535 --> 00:42:40,449
I give you Miss Hilda Whittaker

589
00:42:40,578 --> 00:42:45,698
and, for her debut performance,
Mrs John Whittaker

590
00:42:45,834 --> 00:42:48,997
doing 'The Can-Can'!

591
00:42:49,128 --> 00:42:51,084
Ooh!

592
00:42:55,592 --> 00:42:57,713
Ooh!

593
00:43:10,939 --> 00:43:13,345
