pretending to be someone I'm not.

643
00:47:20,956 --> 00:47:23,788
Especially since it isn't working.

644
00:47:24,750 --> 00:47:28,281
What the devil has that dog dug up?

645
00:47:31,297 --> 00:47:33,371
Pilot, what have you got there?

646
00:47:35,135 --> 00:47:37,505
How could you not tell us?

647
00:47:37,637 --> 00:47:41,085
Marion, it was an accident.
I am walking on eggshells here.

648
00:47:41,223 --> 00:47:45,845
And I believe I panicked.
And once again, I'm very, very sorry.

649
00:47:45,977 --> 00:47:49,308
How could you do it? How could you?

650
00:47:49,439 --> 00:47:54,262
I imagine she lowered her full weight
onto the Chihuahua beneath her.

651
00:47:56,154 --> 00:47:58,228
Marion, please.

652
00:47:58,365 --> 00:48:01,528
John, did you have anything
to do with this?

653
00:48:01,658 --> 00:48:05,569
No. No, I was the sole perpetrator
of Poppy's demise.

654
00:48:05,703 --> 00:48:08,654
And ever since
I have been wracked with guilt.

655
00:48:09,164 --> 00:48:13,158
Please, please, please
let me buy you a new dog.

656
00:48:14,378 --> 00:48:17,411
You might buy your loved ones
in the United States,

657
00:48:17,548 --> 00:48:19,834
but you can't in the United Kingdom.

658
00:48:19,966 --> 00:48:21,293
How unfortunate.

659
00:48:21,426 --> 00:48:25,206
You could at least show some remorse.

660
00:48:25,345 --> 00:48:29,837
I am full of remorse. I just refuse
to invest in amateur theatrics

661
00:48:29,976 --> 00:48:31,598
to convince you of my sincerity.

662
00:48:31,728 --> 00:48:34,928
That's not how I came off
the assembly line. I'm sorry.

663
00:48:35,064 --> 00:48:36,770
I can't change.

664
00:48:36,898 --> 00:48:41,223
Not for you...
not for anybody... any more.

665
00:48:44,239 --> 00:48:47,900
And I wouldn't want her
any other way. So...

666
00:48:51,203 --> 00:48:56,026
Madam, the dog.
- Oh, stay back! Stay back!

667
00:48:57,417 --> 00:49:02,288
I knew it the second
I laid eyes on her. She's a killer.

668
00:49:02,422 --> 00:49:04,578
She sat on poor Poppy deliberately.

669
00:49:04,716 --> 00:49:07,418
Don't be ridiculous.
Of course she didn't.

670
00:49:07,551 --> 00:49:11,959
